ProductName: Suja Organic Mighty Dozen Cold Pressed Juice Drink - 46 fl oz Bottle
Description: Suja Organic Mighty Dozen is a little sweet, a little green and perfectly balanced. This 12 fl oz bottle of green juice will have you feeling mighty good and mighty healthy with 5.5 servings of fruit and vegetables per bottle. Full of organic cold pressed juice from fruits and vegetables with no added sugar, this green juice is an excellent source of vitamin K and a good source of vitamin C. Mighty Dozen blends 12 earthy green with green apple and a lemon and ginger zing for a vibrant organic juice. Sip Suja juice any time to give your body a nutrient boost.
